lead_paragraph: Defending champion Anna Nordqvist overcame a poor start with nine birdies in her last 12 holes for a seven-under-par 64 and a share of the first-round lead at the Shoprite LPGA Classic on Friday in New Jersey.

headline.print_headline: Defending Champion Nordqvist in Three-Way Tie for Lead
